/**
 * Instructions for adding hardware wallet vectors:
 *
 * COLDCARD:
 * 1. Load test seed on Coldcard
 * 2. Navigate to Advanced > Export Wallet > Generic JSON
 * 3. Export to SD card
 * 4. Extract xpub and addresses
 * 5. Verify first few addresses match on-device display
 *
 * LEDGER:
 * 1. Initialize with test seed
 * 2. Use Ledger Live or HWI to export xpub
 * 3. Verify addresses using the device display
 *
 * TREZOR:
 * 1. Initialize with test seed
 * 2. Use Trezor Suite or HWI to export xpub
 * 3. Verify addresses using the device display
 *
 * IMPORTANT: Always use test seeds, never production seeds!
 * The standard test seed is:
 * "abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon abandon about"
 */
